long.en_US:
Are you still annoyed because every time you open iQiyi to watch a video, the opening AD is too long? Well, here comes your savior!

This extension features:
1. Skip the opening advertisement of iQiyi video to say goodbye to your troubles;
2. Count the total number of skip ads, so that you can accurately understand the trouble caused by iQIYI;

The plug-in takes effect immediately after installation and does not require any configuration.
